'''Zanbia ka Fasojamana''' ye jamana datugunen ye [[Kɔrɔnfɛ Afrika]]. Sigiɲɔngɔn jamanaw ye [[Kongo ka Bɛjɛfanga Fasojamana]] saheli fɛ, [[Tanzania]] saheli-kɔrɔn, [[Malawi]] kataa kɔrɔn, [[Mozanbik]], [[Zinbabwe]], [[Botswana]] ani [[Namibia]] kataa worodugu, ani [[Angola]] kataa tlebi. Dugu faaba ye [[Lusaka]] ye a sigilen jaman worodugukɔrɔn. Jamanadenw jugɔsɔlen faaba lamunu la ani Daɲancɛjala yɔrɔ la kataa sahelitlebi.

